explanationofflinedisabled.message: Awuxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi. Ukuze usebenzise i-Google Amadokhumenti ngaphandle koxhumano lwe-inthanethi, iya kokuthi izilungiselelo ekhasini lasekhaya le-Google Amadokhumenti bese uvula ukuvumelanisa okungaxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi ngesikhathi esilandelayo lapho uxhunywe ku-inthanethi.

explanationofflineenabled.message: Awuxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi, kodwa usangakwazi ukuhlela amafayela atholakalayo noma udale amasha.

extdesc.message: Enza izinto zenzeke ungaxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi ngomndeni wemikhiqizo ye-Google Amadokhumenti.

popuphelptext.message: Bhala, hlela, futhi hlanganyela noma yikuphi lapho okhona, unalo noma ungenalo uxhumano lwe-inthanethi.
